3.	Explain encapsulation with following:  Implementation not required
Mobile Phone and Mobile Phone Manufacturer

Encapsulation
Encapsulation is used for binding the data with their member function.Encapsulation also hides the data.
for example mobile phone amd mobile phone manufacturer.mobile phone manufacturer produces mobile on their design.If the user touches the screen
then the screen opens in this the touch is data and mobile phone as object and when the object is created the data binds with   the function of the screen. 
